<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">not really. It does take place around Christmas time (November and on) but Christmas is only mentioned in passing as the town is decorated that way af<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">not really. It does take place around Christmas time (November and on) but Christmas is only mentioned in passing as the town is decorated that way after Thanksgiving and a Christmas dinner is mentioned.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
