        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer107781932" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15815584238117428329">This book was so sugary sweet that I felt like I was reading the Hallmark channel. Yes, I am not that into you! So, in the future, I need to remind myself to stay far away from the pitter patter of love books. Perhaps I am super spoiled by the love story of Ross and Demelza Pollack that I am currently reading, that I find The Sugar Queen to be so implausible that it is laughable.<br/><br/>Sorry Ms Allen, but your books are just not my cup of tea.....without sugar or honey I might add!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


